com.programmerdan.minecraft.civspy

  • Packages that use com.programmerdan.minecraft.civspy 
    Package Description
    com.programmerdan.minecraft.civspy  
    com.programmerdan.minecraft.civspy.listeners
    This package contains one abstract class -- ServerDataListener which must be the superclass of any Listener implementations you want automatically loaded by CivSpy.
    com.programmerdan.minecraft.civspy.listeners.impl  
    com.programmerdan.minecraft.civspy.samplers
    This package contains two abstract classes -- ServerMultiDataSampler or ServerSingleDataSampler -- one of which must be the superclass of any implementations you want automatically loaded by CivSpy.
    com.programmerdan.minecraft.civspy.samplers.impl  
  • Classes in com.programmerdan.minecraft.civspy used by com.programmerdan.minecraft.civspy 
    Class and Description
    CivSpy
    CivSpy is an aggregation platform for vital tracking statistics.
    Config
    Wraps the configuration file for Bukkit.
    DataAggregate
    A data aggregation.
    DataBatcher
    Roughly similar approach to Manager; stage() unwinds data to batch it up, then other task(s) come along to deliver to the database.
    DataManager
    Represents a self-monitoring manager that accepts data into a queue and asynchronously pulls data off and handles aggregation; then passes off to the batcher for database insertion
    DataSample
    A data sample; can be destined for aggregation or stand alone.
    DataSampleKey
    Immutable key, used for aggregations
